headline: 3 Top Dividend Stocks to Buy in March
summary: Investing in dividend stocks can be a great strategy, especially if you pick solid companies that pay reliable and high-yield dividends.  While dividend stocks don't always offer the same excitement as high-flying growth stocks or deep value plays, simple is often more.  Reinvested dividends can compound the growth of a stock holding over time, which can translate into a nice stream of passive income when you choose to start tapping those payouts instead.
